{"tid":2122854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨再次強調沒有計劃實施禁足令 譴責有人三番四次引起恐慌  ( 明明777係記者會自己提起 )","createTime":"2020-07-24T08:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T09:09:40.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0116c3876766d8c58fc908f07c7937e4282f9a1a","tid":2122854,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:38:05.000Z","msg":"政府澄清沒有計劃實施「禁足令」<br />\n<br />\n政府在社交網站再次澄清，沒有計劃實施「禁足令」。政府指，今日再有虛假消息指，行政長官會在下午召開記者會，宣布下星期實施「禁足令」 ，並會停工停市7天，強調絕無此事。<br />\n<br />\n政府強烈譴責一而再、再而三意圖引起公衆恐慌的虛假消息，呼籲市場切勿輕信及傳播謠言。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2348788&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6EngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=ffd45367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348788</a>"},{"pid":"abc3fdd774aef1ba117e7c5f9fcc6258dad1ddcf","tid":2122854,"uid":20170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:40:19.000Z","msg":"其實，好似冇人講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c095d0f214707d4191e27888d50b073d7bff7f91","tid":2122854,"uid":6132,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"abc3fdd774aef1ba117e7c5f9fcc6258dad1ddcf","tid":2122854,"uid":20170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:40:19.000Z","msg":"其實，好似冇人講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:42:32.000Z","msg":"好似係藍絲圍內傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108a1d7d0630caa7d4d307c18b2a38cb7a0f2bdc","tid":2122854,"uid":43062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c095d0f214707d4191e27888d50b073d7bff7f91","tid":2122854,"uid":6132,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"abc3fdd774aef1ba117e7c5f9fcc6258dad1ddcf","tid":2122854,"uid":20170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:40:19.000Z"